## Limitations
The findings are based on available online resources and may not encompass all perspectives on the topic. Some sources lacked specific publication dates, which could affect the currency of the information. Additionally, the complexity of the relationship between language and culture means that this report provides a broad overview rather than an exhaustive analysis. Further research, including empirical studies, would be beneficial to deepen the understanding of this subject.